1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:02,860
Are you there, Charley Bear?
你在吗 查理熊

2
00:00:04,460 --> 00:00:06,280
There you are, Charley!
你来了 查理

3
00:00:07,160 --> 00:00:08,540
What are you doing?
你在做什么

4
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:14,240
Oh, wait. I know. You're measuring how big you are.
哦 等等 我知道了 你在测量你有多大

5
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:20,700
You've grown bigger!
你长大了

6
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:24,620
Oh. You don't think so?
哦 你不这么认为吗

7
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:27,620
Growing takes time. That's all.
成长需要时间 所有的都是

8
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:38,140
Hmm. Standing on your tiptoes doesn't really make you bigger.
嗯 踮起脚尖并不会真的让你变得更大

9
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:45,040
Wow! That's really high jumping, Charley.
哇 跳得真高 查理

10
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:47,360
But it still doesn't make you bigger.
但这并没有让你变大

